Schaefer poured cold water on Frampton&apos;s call to have the third fight in Belfast. 
 
He is unsure if there is a venue which could host the fight, including outdoors at Windsor Park. 
 
Leo Santa Cruz claimed he had talked about quitting to ensure he won. 
